## 🎯 Objectives

* 🔄 Use Enum.each to repeat actions
* 🎨 Use Enum.map to transform lists
* 📋 Work with collections in advanced ways

## 🔄 Enum.each - Do Something with Each Element

```elixir
names = ["Ana", "Peter", "Mary", "Luis"]

Enum.each(names, fn name ->
  IO.puts("Hello, #{name}!")
end)
```

## 🎨 Enum.map - Transform Elements

```elixir
numbers = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]

doubles = Enum.map(numbers, fn number ->
  number * 2
end)

IO.inspect(doubles)
```

## 🎯 Your Turn

