## 🏆 Challenge: Interactive Gallery

```elixir
emojis = ["⭐", "🌟", "✨", "💫", "🌈"]

html = Enum.map(emojis, fn emoji ->
  """
  <div style="display: inline-block; font-size: 60px; margin: 10px;">
    #{emoji}
  </div>
  """
end)
|> Enum.join("")

Kino.Markdown.new("""
<div style="background-color: #1a1a2e; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 15px;">
  #{html}
</div>
""")
```

